data.text:
PRODUCT FEATURES

Features the iconic CU Buffalo logo printed in a repeated pattern

"Colorado" printed in white in a repeated pattern

Leash closure attached to D-ring

Dimensions: 6'

Material composition: Commercial Heavy Grade Webbing

By Spirit Products

Official University of Colorado Licensed Product

PRODUCT DESCRIPTION

Embrace your Colorado pride wherever you wander with our pet leash. Showcasing the iconic CU Buffalo logo, it boasts heavy-grade webbing, a loop handle, and a generous length of 6 feet, catering to all breeds and walking paces. Walk with confidence and style as you represent your favorite team on every outing.
